headline: Tyler Technologies’ State Partners Receive 2024 Government Experience Awards from the Center for Digital Government
summary: PLANO, Texas, December 19, 2024--Tyler Technologies’ state partners in Arkansas and West Virginia received 2024 Government Experience Awards from the Center for Digital Government.
